{"tid":1720511,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【真人真事】今日喺元朗遇到好市民","createTime":"2019-11-14T11:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:12:27.000Z","uid":79122,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"73a9ed817860bd9a3b6f8fda634e53114e0561b0","tid":1720511,"uid":79122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:19:51.000Z","msg":"【真實故事】<br />\n話說小弟住元朗，今日下午出街買餸，<br />\n為咗唔好比人打，專登著咗件紅色T-shirt出街，<br />\n突然迎面而黎兩男兩女，手有香港好市民臂章，<br />\n操流利重口音普通話問路。<br />\n佢地見我著到咁紅，諗住問我應該實冇死，<br />\n小弟當然本住好客既精神，用唔鹹唔淡既普通話，<br />\n有禮地指咗佢地去反方向既地方， <br />\n重講到有咁遠得咁遠， <br />\n重扮哂嘢問佢地要唔要我帶路<br />\n臨走前佢地重好開心講：&quot;謝啦，兄弟！&quot;<br />\n我笑而不語， <br />\n好行， 唔送。"},{"pid":"a86ec360ba5fdb31a863c92ba7fecadc44775ee0","tid":1720511,"uid":79122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:20:39.000Z","msg":"自推， 係咁既局勢比d開心嘢大家舒解下"},{"pid":"9706e1f4f6958cc1a4265c9f0b12505824ffd7bf","tid":1720511,"uid":79122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:25:20.000Z","msg":"自膠"},{"pid":"1d928ae65adae2b8746694ae987cd5d138f6e8d6","tid":1720511,"uid":79122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:34:51.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"9e0c1ee0adaeaa31a2fdc4fbc9a707d42591f33c","tid":1720511,"uid":88222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:20:50.000Z","msg":"幫你推推"},{"pid":"27d3f57bfe816dfe2628d225974624469051044d","tid":1720511,"uid":79122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fdee8b3ccc7806d211b08c1da8fae087724ef03f","tid":1720511,"uid":79122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e0c1ee0adaeaa31a2fdc4fbc9a707d42591f33c","tid":1720511,"uid":88222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:20:50.000Z","msg":"幫你推推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"haha,  thanks"},{"pid":"c004817682794254e82393cc0350e340b4dbacdc","tid":1720511,"uid":79122,"like":0,"dislike":